- Right.

143
00:05:01,149 --> 00:05:02,388
But his character isn't exactly nice.

144
00:05:02,389 --> 00:05:03,619
- Right.
- Okay.

145
00:05:03,659 --> 00:05:07,888
So the drama is about your pursuit of a serial killer?

146
00:05:07,889 --> 00:05:11,228
My character tries to find the real culprit of the serial murder.

147
00:05:11,229 --> 00:05:13,868
But our characters have a history.

148
00:05:13,869 --> 00:05:15,569
It's the same MO.

149
00:05:16,969 --> 00:05:18,398
(The detective chasing "the killer," Park Hae Soo)

150
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,709
There was a scarecrow.

151
00:05:19,809 --> 00:05:20,809
