157
00:05:32,119 --> 00:05:34,519
If we get caught, we'll be the scarecrows.

158
00:05:35,089 --> 00:05:36,759
We end up working together.

159
00:05:37,019 --> 00:05:38,689
- You end up working together?
- Yes.

160
00:05:38,829 --> 00:05:39,929
