It will premiere on April 20 on ENA.

162
00:05:41,929 --> 00:05:43,059
- On ENA.
- Yes.

163
00:05:43,799 --> 00:05:45,598
- That sounds like a good drama.
- It is.

164
00:05:45,599 --> 00:05:46,698
- It does sound like a good one.
- Yes.

